#: s3backend.cpp:41
#, kde-kuit-format
msgctxt "@info"
msgid ""
"Invalid S3 URI, bucket name is missing from the host.<nl/>A valid S3 URI "
"must be written in the form: <link>s3://bucket/key</link>"
msgstr ""
"無效的 S3 URI，主機缺乏儲存貯體名稱。<nl/>有效的 S3 URI 必須使用此格式："
"<link>s3://儲存貯體/金鑰</link>"

#: s3backend.cpp:140 s3backend.cpp:149
#, kde-kuit-format
msgctxt "@info"
msgid "Could not find S3 buckets, please check your AWS configuration."
msgstr "找不到 S3 儲存貯體，請檢查您的 AWS 配置。"

#: s3backend.cpp:622
#, kde-kuit-format
msgctxt "@info"
msgid "Cannot copy between different S3 profiles. Copy the file locally first."
msgstr "無法在不同 S3 設定檔之間複製。請先將檔案複製到本地端。"

#: s3backend.cpp:673
#, kde-kuit-format
msgctxt "@info"
msgid "Could not copy <link>%1</link> to <link>%2</link>"
msgstr "無法複製 <link>%1</link> 到 <link>%2</link>。"

#: s3backend.cpp:748
#, kde-kuit-format
msgctxt "@info"
msgid "Cannot rename between different S3 profiles."
msgstr "無法在不同 S3 設定檔之間重新命名。"

#: s3backend.cpp:877
#, kde-format
msgctxt "@info"
msgid ""
"Some source files could not be deleted after renaming. The renamed folder "
"may still contain leftover files."
msgstr ""
"某些來源檔案在重新命名後無法刪除。重新命名後的資料夾可能仍包含遺留的檔案。"

#: s3backend.cpp:939 s3backend.cpp:1000
#, kde-format
msgctxt "@info"
msgid ""
"Could not retrieve the complete file listing. Some files may not be shown."
msgstr "無法取得完整檔案列表。某些檔案可能沒有被顯示出來。"
